<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="for-one-thing-for-another-thing">for one thing …, for another (thing) …</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>首先 …， 再者…：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>For one thing, reading literary books help to improve my writing skills and broaden my horizons. For another, they can enrich my life.
首先，阅读文学书籍有助于提高我的写作技能并开阔视野。再者，还能丰富我的生活。</p><footer>2012 江西书面表达改</footer></div></div>